Florencia Lozano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Florencia_Lozano 0 Florencia Lozano (born December 16, 1969) is an American actress. She starred as Téa Delgado on the daytime series One Life to Live.Lozano has guest-starred in several primetime television shows, as well as films.
